:"2019-11-21T02:10:34.000Z","msg":"冇紅隧 搭黨鐵俾Raymond 撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hx1KGEP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhx1KGEP.jpg&h=cd6dc7b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"270b32679b926756c87f7ad2e4f79d85530e60fb","tid":1742702,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:12:10.000Z","msg":"明明咁多手足犧牲換取紅隧春袋返來<br />\n依家搞不單事半功倍<br />\n而且可以比更大壓力對面盡快解封紅隧同理大<br />\n問題係我完全見唔到有人做文宣指控政府同黑警包圍理大搞到塞晒<br />\n反而有風向賴落晨早行動度<br />\n晨早運動可以靜靜地贏<br />\n但紅隧停左搞到周圍塞晒要大大力咁講出去<br />\n<br />\n尋晚帶風叫停晨早行動既，你地對唔對得住理大手足<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742715\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742715</a>"},{"pid":"ec855f3d62aee6961e91c6533d1e97bf79b90056","tid":1742702,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:19:31.000Z","msg":"拆左佢, 以後唔好開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa8f531ca26de531dfb5b919c754b0643f147a5","tid":1742702,"uid":211941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:22:58.000Z","msg":"你唔好收錢咪可以即刻行車囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9464b4cfab9d26c458e8f7b4e29f02f300b0759c","tid":1742702,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:26:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不如幫下政府，搞哂三隧，等佢封哂，攬炒!</span>"}]}